  - gender
  - place_of_living
  - country_of_origin
  - description (nullable)
  - classification_result
  - created_at
  - updated_at

### Database Configuration
- Add foreign key relationship (User → Submission)
- Create indexes for:
  - age
  - gender
  - place_of_living
  - country_of_origin
  - created_at

